        By accessing or using our website at 8eyetiedye.com (the "Site"), you
        agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not
        agree to these Terms, do not use the Site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        1. Eligibility
      </h2>
      <p>
        You must be at least 13 years old to use the Site. Users under 18 may
        browse and generate designs but may not make purchases. You must be at
