          creates the patterns.
        </li>
        <li>
          Each design is generated once and is unique. We do not guarantee the
          ability to reproduce any specific design.
        </li>
        <li>
          Generated designs expire after 24 hours. If you do not purchase a
          design within that window, it is permanently deleted and cannot be
          recovered.
        </li>
        <li>
          You do not acquire copyright ownership of AI-generated designs.
          Designs are provided for personal use on purchased merchandise only.
        </li>
        <li>
          We reserve the right to limit the number of free design generations
          per session or per day.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        3. Products and Orders
      </h2>
