        All products sold on 8EyeTieDye are manufactured on demand through
        print-on-demand partners. By placing an order, you acknowledge and agree
        that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          Products are made to order and cannot be canceled once production has
          begun.
        </li>
        <li>
          Colors may vary slightly between the on-screen preview and the printed
