        </li>
        <li>
          Production and shipping times are estimates and may vary. We are not
          responsible for delays caused by our fulfillment partners or shipping
          carriers.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not accept returns for buyer's remorse or change of mind. If you
          receive a defective or damaged product, contact us within 14 days of
          delivery for a replacement.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        4. Payments and Pricing
      </h2>
      <p>
        All prices are listed in United States Dollars (USD). Payments are
        processed securely through Stripe. By making a purchase, you agree that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          You authorize us to charge the payment method you provide for the
          total amount of your order, including applicable taxes and shipping.
        </li>
        <li>
          Refunds are not available once a product has entered production. If
